         <notesStmt>
            <note>Stains and tidemarks from damp, especially on first and last few leaves. Slight rodent damage at bottom corner in part. Ink blurred in parts. Foredge of paper ends rolling. Small tears. Lacuna after folio 132.</note>
            <note>Duke of Sussex plate with his coat of arms, pasted on the inner front cover.A note of acquisition of the manuscript in French, dated 1774, folio 2v.An English desciption of the manuscript, in pencil, folio 1v.</note>
